
1. Creating a new message: Follow the steps as described below.
       a) without data - this is also referred to as signal.
             All you need to do is to insert your new message name into MessageType enum in message_type.py
       b) with data - To create a new message with data, you need to insert
             i) insert your new message name into MessageType enum in message_type.py
            ii) create a capnp structure with the needed data fields under capnp_impl/capnp_struct sub-directory 
           iii) insert your message name and capnp structure into the message_capnp dict in capnp_impl/capnp_impl.py

2. Using the existing message in your application: Use APIs described in message.py
       
